ribute developments correctly. risk must begin with Low, Medium or High then a short rationale. For movers, use the LEADERSHIP/BOARD CHANGES DIGEST and include every appointment, resignation, promotion or board change; when a mover's name, previous role, new role or date is not stated, set that field to 'Not specified'. If a PREVIOUS EDITION SUMMARY is provided, make the brief week-over-week aware: populate weekOverWeek with the key changes since then and reflect momentum versus last edition in signals where relevant. Output ONLY the JSON object."},
